-------- KEYS --------
targetname : activating trigger points to this.
name : Name of the way that the gamer will see when he crosses the start line.
type : Way number for alternate routes.
total : Players will need to acquire this amount of points before they can finish the run, at this jumpstop.</integer>
color: If not used, it will default to white.
Valid color numbers are:
	0: white (default)
	1 : red
	2 : green
	3 : yellow
	4 : blue
	5 : cyan
	6 : magenta
	7 : white
	8 : orange (bugged)
	9 : olive (bugged)
*/